<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2025-01-09T14:04:05-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2025-01-09T14:04:05-05:00</published><updated> 2025-01-09T14:04:05-05:00</updated><title>如何删除您的 Facebook 帐户</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Facebook 符号，背景为代表社交网络的各种图标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UtqMxDsQdUMvgRDlF_hL2p7Y3u0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/68672679/HT009_facebook_0008.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Samar Haddad / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;fDVj0X&quot;>;您可能想知道如何删除您的 Facebook 帐户，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/24339131/meta-content-moderation-fact-check-zuckerberg-texas&quot;>;事实检查不再被认为重要&lt;/a>;，Meta 正在改变其&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/7/24338471/meta-hate-speech-hateful-conduct-policy-moderation&quot;>;仇恨行为的定义&lt;/a>;。这很容易做到，我们将向您展示如何操作。但是，您应该先下载所有内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;fCaD7i&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;元和的社交网络替代方案厌恶马斯克&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23429095/twitter-social-network-alternatives-mastodon-reddit-tumblr-cohost&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;lTH5PB&quot;>;以下说明适用于 Facebook 的网页版，但您可以在移动应用程序上遵循几乎相同的顺序。&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;2bSQ1Y&quot;>;下载您的档案&lt;/h2>; &lt;p id=&quot;Fv7htI&quot;>;您的 Facebook 档案仅包含&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/help/405183566203254?helpref=faq_content&quot; >;与您的帐户相关的所有相关信息&lt;/a>;，包括您的照片、活动会话、聊天记录、IP 地址、面部识别数据以及您点击的广告。这是您应该保存的个人信息。&lt;/p>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;tB7vax&quot;>;点击右上角的个人图标。 &lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;Kt1gj6&quot;>;前往&lt;strong>;设置与设置隐私&lt;/strong>; >; &lt;strong>;设置&lt;/strong>;。 &lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;4Oo0T9&quot;>;点击左侧的&lt;strong>;帐户中心&lt;/strong>;框。&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;屏幕截图：Meta&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;帐户中心是您可以下载信息和删除帐户的地方。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;wlvZue &quot;>;转到&lt;strong>;您的左侧的信息和权限&lt;/strong>;，然后&lt;strong>;下载您的信息>;下载或传输信息。&lt;/strong>; &lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;5pcPYR&quot;>;您可以选择从 Facebook 或 Instagram 帐户（或两者）传输信息。 &lt;/li>; &lt;li id=&quot;B0P9qJ&quot;>;您现在拥有...&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22231495/delete-facebook -page-account-how-to&quot;>;在 The Verge 上阅读完整故事。&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/22231495/delete-facebook-page-account-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/22231495/delete-facebook-page-account-how-to</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name><name>米卡·辛格尔顿</name></author></entry><entry><published>2025-01-09T13:52:35-05:00</published><updated> 2025-01-09T13:52:35-05:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的健身追踪器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple Watch、Garmin Epix、Fitbit 和 Amazfit Bip 健身追踪器采用风格化的蓝色背景。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9NfU5CzAkm1H45234kKpT8gicKk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x8 73/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70657030/acastro_220321_5092_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从简单的健身手环和坚固耐用的运动手表到戒指，这些都是您可以获得的最佳追踪器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p >;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker&quot;>;在 The Verge 上阅读完整故事。&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2025-01-09T13:49:06-05:00</published><updated> 2025-01-09T13:49:06-05:00</updated><title>谷歌和微软各为特朗普就职典礼捐赠100万美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 图像的照片拼贴，背后是图形、故障设计。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fNB-noPHuZxM3tYjESZarmrzxII=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/ cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73836915/STK175_DONALD_TRUMP_CVIRGINIA_D.0.jpg&quot; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;kehgSO&quot;>;谷歌和微软是最新为当选总统唐纳德·特朗普就职典礼捐款的科技公司。每家公司向该基金捐款 100 万美元，与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/12/24319768/meta-1-million-donation-trump-inauguration&quot;>; 承诺的金额相同元&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/12/24320063/amazon-is-donating-1-million-to-trumps-inauguration&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/13/24320643/sam-altman-is-donating-to-trumps-inauguration-too&quot;>;山姆·奥尔特曼&lt;/a>;，和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/3/24335290/apple-donation-donald-trump-inauguration-tim-cook&quot;>;蒂姆·库克&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;hqz7eN&quot;>;在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F01%2F09%2Fgoogle-donates-1-million-to -特朗普-伊诺古ration-fund.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2025%2F1%2F9%2F24340039%2Fgoogle-microsoft-trump-inauguration-donation&quot;谷歌全球政府事务和公共政策主管卡兰·巴蒂亚 (Karan Bhatia) 在向 CNBC 发表的声明中表示，该公司将通过 YouTube 直播和直接直播来支持就职典礼。我们主页上的链接”，并提供财政捐助。此次捐赠可能是谷歌赢得特朗普支持的更大战略的一部分，特朗普&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/15/24271297/google-donald-trump-bananas-breaking-up -bananas&quot;>;威胁要拆分科技巨头&lt;/a>;或&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/5/24212296/trump-vance-google-shut-down-first-amendment&quot;>;完全关闭&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt; p id=&quot;LGa2Yp&quot;>;微软也捐赠了100万美元，此前为特朗普首次就职典礼捐赠了50万美元，并为总统乔·拜登的就职典礼捐赠了相同金额基金公司发言人&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F01%2F09%2Fmicrosoft-contributes-1-million-to -胜出-在auguration-fund.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2025%2F1%2F9%2F24340039%2Fgoogle-microsoft-trump-inauguration-donation&quot; rel=&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;告诉 CNBC&lt;/a>;。据 CNBC 报道，微软首席执行官萨蒂亚·纳德拉 (Satya Nadella) 曾多次与特朗普会面，并参与了 2020 年收购 TikTok 的谈判，当时特朗普试图在美国禁止该应用。&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/9/24340039/google-microsoft-trump-inauguration-donation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/9/24340039/google-microsoft-trump-inauguration-donation</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2025-01-09T13:45:23-05:00</published><updated> 2025-01-09T13:45:23-05:00</updated><title> 《最后生还者 第二部》PC 版也需要 PSN 帐户</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《最后生还者第二部重制版》截图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4M-TzTj60uSX9xM46GBc6kDGNrc=/0x0:1620x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73836910/tlou_part2_remaster.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Naughty Dog&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;IzVq7m&quot;>;&lt;em>;《最后生还者：第二部分》&lt;/em>;重制版&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;即将加入 PlayStation Network 俱乐部。这意味着，如果您在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/app/2531310/The_Last_of_Us_Part_II_Remastered/&quot;>;Steam&lt;/a>; 上购买游戏后想玩该游戏，则需要关联 PSN 帐户、&lt;a href=&quot;https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/the-last-of-us-part-ii-remastered&quot;>;Epic Games&lt;/a>; 以及其他 PC 平台在 4 月份推出时，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/the-last-of-us-part-2-on-pc-will-require-a-psn- account/&quot;>;正如 &lt;em>;Video Games Chronicle&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 之前发现的那样。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;FUKuds&quot;>;事实证明，这一要求在 PC 上发布的其他索尼游戏中非常不受欢迎，包括&lt;一href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/11/24154412/steam-refunding-ghost-of-tsushima-preorders-psn-network-unavailable&quot;>;&lt;em>;对马岛之魂&lt;/em>; &lt;/一>;，&lt;一href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/30/24168284/god-of-war-ragnarok-on-pc-requires-a-psn-account&quot;>;&lt;em>;战神诸神黄昏&lt; /em>;&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/5/24263038/youll-need-a-psn-account-to-play-the-horizo​​n-zero-dawn-remaster-on-pc&quot;>; &lt;em>;地平线零之曙光&lt;/em>;重制&lt;/a>;。去年，《Helldiver》突然引入 PSN 帐户链接后，《Helldiver》玩家对这款游戏进行了评论轰炸，导致索尼&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24150327/sony-helldivers-2 -review-bombing-psn-login&quot;>;完全回到要求&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;img alt=&quot; &quot; data-mask-text=&quot;false&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eCS8KRoWa0Gf9wCiEVqaqe7juCQ=/400x0/filters:no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25824354/tlou_part_2_psn.png&quot;>; &lt; cite>;屏幕截图：Steam&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;sRI1dn&quot;>;目前还不清楚为什么索尼需要 PSN 帐户才能玩《最后生还者第 2 部分》&lt;/em>;，因为它没有任何多人游戏功能，而且该要求还可能会阻止数十个不支持 PSN 的国家/地区的人们玩该游戏。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;b02kFD&quot;>;&lt;em>;《最后生还者 第 2 部分》重制版在 PC 上发布4月3日为49.99 美元。&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/9/24340000/the-last-of-us-part-2-pc-playstation-network" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/9/24340000/the-last-of-us-part-2-pc-playstation-network</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2025-01-09T13:26:01-05:00</published><updated> 2025-01-09T13:26:01-05:00</updated><title>谍照似乎显示特斯拉更新后的 Model Y 正在测试中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;银色新车型y前部在雪地行驶&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4TTSHbgz9DLKgVv8E0WX5ptAKdo=/0x0:1026x684/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73836865/Gg1f09LWcAAbzcJ.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;哦嘿，另一个全正面灯条设计。&lt;/em>; |图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/DEmPZkXIZl4/?img_index=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Cochespias1&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/图>; &lt;p id=&quot;5ltC